1
00:00:11,670 --> 00:00:12,670
For the first medicine,

2
00:00:12,490 --> 00:00:15,330
[2015] [Department of Psychiatry]

3
00:00:12,880 --> 00:00:14,960
half a pill a day keeps your mood stable.

4
00:00:14,960 --> 00:00:16,190
Within half an hour to an hour,

5
00:00:16,190 --> 00:00:17,650
you'll fall right asleep.

6
00:00:18,320 --> 00:00:19,550
It'll affect my work.

7
00:00:20,670 --> 00:00:21,670
Professor Jiang,

8
00:00:21,920 --> 00:00:24,390
you can stop thinking
about your work for now.

9
00:00:24,390 --> 00:00:26,450
Clear your mind, calm your emotions,

10
00:00:26,710 --> 00:00:28,670
and ease your nerves.

11
00:00:28,670 --> 00:00:29,230
Okay?

12
00:00:30,840 --> 00:00:32,840
Well, there is another option,

13
00:00:32,870 --> 00:00:34,390
the one we talked about last time.

14
00:00:34,390 --> 00:00:36,720
This medicine can be taken continuously.

15
00:00:36,790 --> 00:00:38,850
Take two pills for the first two days,

16
00:00:38,910 --> 00:00:40,230
then we'll see.

17
00:00:40,260 --> 00:00:41,790
If the situation improves,

18
00:00:42,150 --> 00:00:43,240
we can reduce the dosage appropriately.

19
00:00:43,240 --> 00:00:45,240
But many of my patients have reported

20
00:00:45,240 --> 00:00:47,560
that this medicine
has certain side effects.

21
00:00:47,560 --> 00:00:49,220
It'll affect my mental agility...

22
00:00:49,220 --> 00:00:49,990
I told you.

23
00:00:50,280 --> 00:00:52,010
Stop thinking about your work.

24
00:00:56,480 --> 00:00:58,010
It'll give you nightmares.

25
00:01:01,110 --> 00:01:02,280
I'll take this one.

26
00:01:03,420 --> 00:01:04,560
Your current condition

27
00:01:04,560 --> 00:01:06,230
is very serious.

28
00:01:07,000 --> 00:01:10,130
Let's first take the one
that can stabilize you quickly.

29
00:01:11,220 --> 00:01:12,560
I'll prescribe it for you.

30
00:01:12,560 --> 00:01:14,000
Take it when you need to.

31
00:01:14,200 --> 00:01:16,000
Don't skip it just because

32
00:01:16,200 --> 00:01:17,400
you're afraid
that it might affect your thinking

33
00:01:17,400 --> 00:01:18,560
or slow you down.

34
00:01:19,360 --> 00:01:21,140
I've seen many people like you.

35
00:01:21,760 --> 00:01:22,840
I'll say it again.

36
00:01:23,400 --> 00:01:24,430
Pushing your brain too hard

37
00:01:24,430 --> 00:01:27,000
takes a heavy toll on you.

38
00:01:28,150 --> 00:01:29,120
Professor Jiang,

39
00:01:29,120 --> 00:01:31,400
staying healthy and staying alive

40
00:01:31,710 --> 00:01:33,910
are much more important than your work.

41
00:01:34,280 --> 00:01:34,840
Okay.

42
00:02:54,329 --> 00:03:00,030
[Sunsets Secrets Regrets]

43
00:03:00,360 --> 00:03:02,780
[Episode 8]

44
00:03:19,270 --> 00:03:22,840
[Team Furis VS Team Jiabotubo]

45
00:03:28,829 --> 00:03:31,130
[Wangtu Scrap Yard]

46
00:03:43,770 --> 00:03:44,310
Police!

47
00:03:44,430 --> 00:03:44,890
Freeze!

48
00:03:44,890 --> 00:03:45,350
Freeze!

49
00:03:47,079 --> 00:03:47,680
Don't move!

50
00:03:47,680 --> 00:03:48,150
Police!

51
00:03:48,520 --> 00:03:49,180
Don't move!

52
00:03:49,470 --> 00:03:49,870
Freeze!

53
00:03:49,870 --> 00:03:50,870
Police! Stop!

54
00:03:51,150 --> 00:03:52,280
Police!

55
00:03:54,760 --> 00:03:55,329
Don't run!

56
00:03:55,329 --> 00:03:55,790
Freeze!

57
00:03:56,520 --> 00:03:57,120
Don't run!

58
00:03:59,070 --> 00:03:59,790
Here! Right here!

59
00:03:59,790 --> 00:04:00,650
Take them away!

60
00:04:09,910 --> 00:04:10,570
Reporting.

61
00:04:10,670 --> 00:04:12,000
Mission accomplished.

62
00:04:15,060 --> 00:04:15,840
Cheng.

63
00:04:16,560 --> 00:04:17,620
What are you doing?

64
00:04:18,350 --> 00:04:19,680
Having... having a late-night snack.

65
00:04:19,680 --> 00:04:20,490
I told you to stay on lookout.

66
00:04:20,490 --> 00:04:21,829
Why are you having snack?

67
00:04:21,829 --> 00:04:22,430
No, Cheng.

68
00:04:22,480 --> 00:04:24,600
We happened to pass by
a famous barbecue place.

69
00:04:24,600 --> 00:04:25,360
It tastes good.

70
00:04:25,360 --> 00:04:27,090
We figured we'd bring you some.

71
00:04:27,450 --> 00:04:28,580
Come back when you're finished.

72
00:04:28,580 --> 00:04:29,380
Stop tailing.

73
00:04:29,750 --> 00:04:30,720
No, Cheng.

74
00:04:30,950 --> 00:04:31,840
We know we were wrong.

75
00:04:31,840 --> 00:04:32,800
We'll go back to tailing

76
00:04:32,800 --> 00:04:34,060
right after we finish.

77
00:04:34,860 --> 00:04:36,210
I told you to stop tailing.

78
00:04:36,210 --> 00:04:37,740
That place has been busted.

79
00:04:38,870 --> 00:04:39,390
Wait.

80
00:04:39,600 --> 00:04:40,400
Did we do it?

81
00:04:41,170 --> 00:04:42,700
What are you talking about?

82
00:04:42,710 --> 00:04:43,850
We don't have the ability to do that,

83
00:04:43,850 --> 00:04:44,460
okay?

84
00:04:55,040 --> 00:04:55,830
Remember.

85
00:04:57,360 --> 00:04:58,340
Don't give your opponent

86
00:04:58,340 --> 00:05:00,310
any chance to succeed.

87
00:05:02,900 --> 00:05:05,700
Pin them to the ground
and wipe the floor with them.

88
00:05:07,060 --> 00:05:08,380
At the end of the day,

89
00:05:09,750 --> 00:05:11,810
you police are the ones I can count on.

90
00:05:12,440 --> 00:05:15,390
Boss, that doesn't
sound like a compliment.

91
00:05:19,950 --> 00:05:20,690
But boss,

92
00:05:21,660 --> 00:05:24,590
now that Old Scorpion's new channel
has been busted,

93
00:05:24,890 --> 00:05:26,650
will he really go back to us?

94
00:05:29,000 --> 00:05:31,000
We've been in this for so many years.

95
00:05:31,350 --> 00:05:33,300
He can't just toss us aside.

96
00:05:34,890 --> 00:05:35,810
Let me tell you.

97
00:05:36,600 --> 00:05:39,120
If the goods get stuck in their own hands,

98
00:05:40,470 --> 00:05:41,909
they would suffer too.

99
00:05:43,510 --> 00:05:44,430
Tell me,

100
00:05:44,830 --> 00:05:45,960
what's on your mind?

101
00:05:47,680 --> 00:05:49,270
First, let them get anxious.

102
00:05:49,270 --> 00:05:50,270
Then,

103
00:05:51,270 --> 00:05:53,390
we offer them some new plans.

104
00:05:53,980 --> 00:05:56,980
We give them what they want
and provide what they need.

105
00:06:00,310 --> 00:06:00,920
Boss,

106
00:06:02,130 --> 00:06:03,930
I heard from Qiu Ye

107
00:06:03,960 --> 00:06:05,090
that Old Scorpion

108
00:06:05,610 --> 00:06:07,140
lost a very important young man

109
00:06:07,140 --> 00:06:09,000
under his command five years ago.

110
00:06:11,430 --> 00:06:12,070
So?

111
00:06:13,140 --> 00:06:15,410
That means Old Scorpion values talent.

112
00:06:15,970 --> 00:06:17,170
So?

113
00:06:18,560 --> 00:06:20,120
I'm a young man.

114
00:06:22,920 --> 00:06:23,720
Cheng,

115
00:06:24,440 --> 00:06:26,170
you've got quite the ambition.

116
00:06:32,370 --> 00:06:34,370
Boss, I'll still say the same thing.

117
00:06:34,780 --> 00:06:36,130
You brought me into this business.

118
00:06:36,130 --> 00:06:37,460
So no matter how far I go,

119
00:06:37,480 --> 00:06:39,480
I'll only answer to the He brothers.

120
00:06:39,800 --> 00:06:41,040
But what I can't stomach now

121
00:06:41,040 --> 00:06:42,580
is that Lai San has taken all the meat

122
00:06:42,580 --> 00:06:43,480
and left me with just the bone.

123
00:06:43,480 --> 00:06:44,810
That's not right, is it?

124
00:06:45,310 --> 00:06:46,480
Now that things are tense,

125
00:06:46,480 --> 00:06:47,310
the market is bad,

126
00:06:47,310 --> 00:06:48,860
and Old Scorpion still has that attitude,

127
00:06:48,860 --> 00:06:50,659
I have to figure out a way myself.

128
00:06:51,940 --> 00:06:54,270
Since there's someone in his inner circle

129
00:06:54,620 --> 00:06:56,480
who is willing to show me the ropes,

130
00:06:56,480 --> 00:06:58,390
whatever Lai San cost you,

131
00:06:58,480 --> 00:06:59,610
I'll make it all back

132
00:06:59,630 --> 00:07:00,690
for you.

133
00:07:05,000 --> 00:07:06,460
It just depends on whether

134
00:07:06,680 --> 00:07:08,540
you are willing to bet on me, boss.

135
00:07:13,190 --> 00:07:14,600
Don't tell me

136
00:07:15,630 --> 00:07:17,290
you haven't slept with Qiu Ye.

137
00:07:19,040 --> 00:07:20,470
I'm taking a break.

138
00:07:22,900 --> 00:07:23,820
Maybe later.

139
00:07:32,840 --> 00:07:35,450
[Tomb of the Martyr, Zhou Chuan]

140
00:07:37,630 --> 00:07:39,630
I'll leave you two alone for a while.

141
00:07:57,659 --> 00:07:58,250
Chuan.

142
00:08:02,340 --> 00:08:03,050
I'm here.

143
00:08:04,740 --> 00:08:06,600
The weather is really nice today.

144
00:08:06,860 --> 00:08:08,860
Let's enjoy the sunshine together.

145
00:08:11,370 --> 00:08:12,280
We had a lead

146
00:08:12,620 --> 00:08:13,280
on the case,

147
00:08:15,110 --> 00:08:16,370
but it went cold again.

148
00:08:16,500 --> 00:08:17,820
But don't worry.

149
00:08:18,650 --> 00:08:20,650
I'll definitely keep following it.

150
00:08:21,580 --> 00:08:22,390
Two days ago,

151
00:08:22,460 --> 00:08:24,590
Wei told me there was new information.

152
00:08:25,270 --> 00:08:26,330
I'll keep looking.

153
00:08:27,750 --> 00:08:30,010
I'll definitely figure everything out.

154
00:08:32,870 --> 00:08:33,630
By the way,

155
00:08:33,909 --> 00:08:34,789
yesterday,

156
00:08:35,419 --> 00:08:36,700
I saw Wei and Bin.

157
00:08:38,179 --> 00:08:39,150
Especially Bin,

158
00:08:39,230 --> 00:08:40,470
he has really made something of himself.

159
00:08:40,470 --> 00:08:41,870
He even opened a restaurant.

160
00:08:41,870 --> 00:08:43,200
It's pretty delicious.

161
00:08:43,820 --> 00:08:45,080
Wei is also doing well.

162
00:08:45,510 --> 00:08:47,780
He successfully joined
the Provincial Bureau.

163
00:08:47,780 --> 00:08:49,910
And he's going to be a father this fall.

164
00:08:53,390 --> 00:08:54,590
Time flies

165
00:08:55,420 --> 00:08:56,700
so fast.

166
00:08:57,990 --> 00:08:59,520
I still remember last year,

167
00:08:59,870 --> 00:09:00,990
he sighed to me,

168
00:09:03,660 --> 00:09:05,990
saying that back when you were still here,

169
00:09:06,750 --> 00:09:08,610
they all saw you as the role model.

170
00:09:09,350 --> 00:09:11,550
They wanted to match you in everything.

171
00:09:13,110 --> 00:09:14,420
Training,

172
00:09:15,590 --> 00:09:16,900
work,

173
00:09:18,060 --> 00:09:19,320
even their love lives.

174
00:09:20,110 --> 00:09:21,770
They all wanted to be like you.

175
00:09:25,510 --> 00:09:26,590
Me too.

176
00:09:27,270 --> 00:09:27,900
Chuan,

177
00:09:32,510 --> 00:09:34,370
you've always been my role model.

178
00:09:41,400 --> 00:09:42,040
Chuan,

179
00:09:43,120 --> 00:09:44,480
I miss you.

180
00:09:45,870 --> 00:09:47,120
If only

181
00:09:49,980 --> 00:09:51,110
you were still here.

182
00:09:57,100 --> 00:09:58,010
Enough of that.

183
00:10:08,860 --> 00:10:10,650
Take a look over there.

184
00:10:12,150 --> 00:10:13,260
See that guy?

185
00:10:14,040 --> 00:10:15,570
He's standing right there.

186
00:10:17,530 --> 00:10:18,690
I married him.

187
00:10:21,270 --> 00:10:22,200
Jiang Hansheng.

188
00:10:25,390 --> 00:10:26,850
Do you still remember him?

189
00:10:28,840 --> 00:10:30,560
He used to live next door to us.

190
00:10:33,270 --> 00:10:34,670
He treats me really well.

191
00:10:36,110 --> 00:10:37,040
Mom and Dad

192
00:10:37,630 --> 00:10:38,870
both like him a lot.

193
00:10:41,270 --> 00:10:41,920
Chuan,

194
00:10:43,350 --> 00:10:44,950
you can rest easy now, right?

195
00:10:45,470 --> 00:10:46,600
I'm doing very well.

196
00:11:01,030 --> 00:11:02,100
Am I interrupting?

197
00:11:03,860 --> 00:11:04,740
No.

198
00:11:04,770 --> 00:11:07,030
I was just introducing you to my brother.

199
00:11:07,610 --> 00:11:08,540
Is he satisfied?

200
00:11:10,000 --> 00:11:11,200
He is very satisfied.

201
00:11:11,840 --> 00:11:12,570
That's good.

202
00:11:13,200 --> 00:11:13,800
Let's go.

203
00:11:16,950 --> 00:11:18,480
I have something to say too.

204
00:11:18,880 --> 00:11:19,400
Okay.

205
00:11:19,920 --> 00:11:21,400
I'll go start the car then.

206
00:11:39,820 --> 00:11:40,340
Chuan,

207
00:11:41,830 --> 00:11:43,160
I'm visiting you again.

208
00:11:44,050 --> 00:11:46,660
This is the first time
Zhou Jin and I came to see you together.

209
00:11:46,660 --> 00:11:47,920
We are both doing well.

210
00:11:48,890 --> 00:11:50,550
Mom and Dad are doing well too.

211
00:11:52,240 --> 00:11:53,050
Don't worry,

212
00:11:54,470 --> 00:11:56,870
I'll definitely
take good care of Zhou Jin.

213
00:12:32,930 --> 00:12:33,650
Zhou Jin.

214
00:12:38,200 --> 00:12:38,930
Zhou Jin!

215
00:12:47,430 --> 00:12:48,030
Hansheng!

216
00:12:48,080 --> 00:12:48,880
What's wrong?

217
00:12:49,400 --> 00:12:50,330
Jiang Hansheng.

218
00:12:50,640 --> 00:12:51,900
What's wrong with you?

219
00:12:52,280 --> 00:12:52,880
I'm sorry.

220
00:12:53,000 --> 00:12:54,250
Sorry for what?

221
00:12:54,470 --> 00:12:56,270
Okay. The day before yesterday,

222
00:12:56,290 --> 00:12:57,500
I thought I crossed the line

223
00:12:57,500 --> 00:12:58,700
and it was my problem!

224
00:12:58,830 --> 00:12:59,620
But today,

225
00:13:00,210 --> 00:13:00,930
we're even!

226
00:13:01,640 --> 00:13:02,310
Bin.

227
00:13:03,160 --> 00:13:03,830
Bin!

228
00:13:37,670 --> 00:13:38,600
Jiang Hansheng,

229
00:13:38,880 --> 00:13:40,140
I need an explanation.

230
00:13:42,710 --> 00:13:44,440
I mistook him for someone else.

231
00:13:45,190 --> 00:13:46,720
Who did you mistake him for?

232
00:14:10,190 --> 00:14:11,050
Anti-anxiety?

233
00:14:12,000 --> 00:14:13,330
Why are you taking this?

234
00:14:13,390 --> 00:14:15,520
And why do you always
keep it in the car?

235
00:14:18,040 --> 00:14:19,100
I'm not a criminal.

236
00:14:19,710 --> 00:14:20,950
I never said you were.

237
00:14:22,040 --> 00:14:23,970
But I don't want someone close to me

238
00:14:24,550 --> 00:14:25,400
to lie to me.

239
00:14:26,790 --> 00:14:29,390
I won't ask about things
you don't want to tell.

240
00:14:29,430 --> 00:14:30,430
But I want to know,

241
00:14:30,920 --> 00:14:32,670
when you pushed Yan Bin just now,

242
00:14:32,670 --> 00:14:34,470
what exactly were you thinking?

243
00:14:34,830 --> 00:14:35,690
To protect you.

244
00:14:42,430 --> 00:14:43,430
So,

245
00:14:46,160 --> 00:14:46,950
you mistook him

246
00:14:46,950 --> 00:14:47,950
for someone else.

247
00:14:48,880 --> 00:14:50,610
You think someone will hurt me.

248
00:14:52,000 --> 00:14:53,060
Who is that person?

249
00:15:09,920 --> 00:15:10,470
Zhou Jin.

250
00:15:14,160 --> 00:15:16,490
I used to carry out some special missions.

251
00:15:16,830 --> 00:15:17,960
They left me on edge.

252
00:15:20,000 --> 00:15:21,520
You weren't just some researcher

253
00:15:21,520 --> 00:15:23,470
back at the Provincial Bureau, right?

254
00:15:23,470 --> 00:15:24,280
Otherwise, they wouldn't have let you

255
00:15:24,280 --> 00:15:25,880
carry out special missions.

256
00:15:26,520 --> 00:15:28,580
You've worked on the front lines too.

257
00:15:33,830 --> 00:15:35,160
What exactly were they?

258
00:15:35,920 --> 00:15:36,780
What missions?

259
00:15:39,190 --> 00:15:40,120
Are there rules?

260
00:15:40,760 --> 00:15:41,760
So you can't tell?

261
00:15:55,920 --> 00:15:56,470
Zhou Jin,

262
00:15:57,160 --> 00:15:58,090
I won't hurt you,

263
00:15:58,710 --> 00:16:00,570
and I won't hurt innocent people.

264
00:16:00,830 --> 00:16:01,760
Don't be afraid,

265
00:16:02,310 --> 00:16:02,920
okay?

266
00:16:07,640 --> 00:16:08,840
Why would I be afraid?

267
00:16:13,000 --> 00:16:14,920
It's just that I don't know you
well enough,

268
00:16:14,920 --> 00:16:15,850
Jiang Hansheng.

269
00:16:17,120 --> 00:16:18,520
I only found out recently

270
00:16:18,670 --> 00:16:20,710
that you used to work
at the Provincial Bureau.

271
00:16:20,710 --> 00:16:22,570
There are many major cases there.

272
00:16:23,590 --> 00:16:25,830
Front-line work, no matter where you are,

273
00:16:25,830 --> 00:16:27,030
is always dangerous.

274
00:16:28,670 --> 00:16:29,240
I get it.

275
00:16:36,530 --> 00:16:38,530
They're just your stress responses

276
00:16:38,710 --> 00:16:39,780
and muscle memory.

277
00:16:41,590 --> 00:16:42,470
I understand.

278
00:16:45,640 --> 00:16:46,170
However,

279
00:16:47,880 --> 00:16:49,240
I'm not an ordinary person.

280
00:16:49,240 --> 00:16:50,300
I'm a policewoman.

281
00:16:51,000 --> 00:16:52,190
Don't do that again,

282
00:16:52,880 --> 00:16:53,280
okay?

283
00:16:55,350 --> 00:16:56,350
As for criminals,

284
00:16:58,000 --> 00:16:59,730
if they dare to lay a hand on you,

285
00:17:00,280 --> 00:17:02,140
I'll show them what the runner-up

286
00:17:03,640 --> 00:17:05,119
of the police academy combat competition

287
00:17:05,119 --> 00:17:06,089
is capable of.

288
00:17:12,119 --> 00:17:12,710
Zhou Jin.

289
00:17:14,839 --> 00:17:17,640
This is the first time
you've hugged me on your own.

290
00:17:19,560 --> 00:17:20,160
Is it?

291
00:17:25,470 --> 00:17:26,069
Thank you.

292
00:17:57,810 --> 00:18:01,200
[Zhao Xiaoyu]
[Resident of Lishui Residential Area]

293
00:18:08,270 --> 00:18:09,000
Are you okay?

294
00:18:11,910 --> 00:18:13,430
I'm fine. Thanks.

295
00:18:25,210 --> 00:18:26,270
You drank too much.

296
00:18:27,670 --> 00:18:29,600
It's dangerous to stay here alone.

297
00:18:30,400 --> 00:18:31,330
I want to go home.

298
00:18:33,120 --> 00:18:34,250
Are you in a bad mood?

299
00:18:42,840 --> 00:18:44,300
Is your home far from here?

300
00:18:45,190 --> 00:18:45,750
Yes.

301
00:18:54,030 --> 00:18:55,070
Your clothes

302
00:18:58,030 --> 00:18:59,090
feel comfortable.

303
00:19:09,560 --> 00:19:10,920
Let me take you home.

304
00:19:22,710 --> 00:19:23,240
Let's go.

305
00:19:27,130 --> 00:19:27,810
Slow down.

306
00:19:32,030 --> 00:19:33,320
Your red dress

307
00:19:35,360 --> 00:19:37,090
seems to be missing something.

308
00:19:52,770 --> 00:19:53,660
Door unlocked.

309
00:19:53,680 --> 00:19:54,870
Welcome home.

310
00:20:00,510 --> 00:20:01,190
Sir.

311
00:20:01,430 --> 00:20:03,630
All this time off has made you lazy, huh?

312
00:20:04,880 --> 00:20:06,920
No, I'm ready to get back to work anytime.

313
00:20:06,220 --> 00:20:07,670
[Wang Pengze]

314
00:20:08,230 --> 00:20:08,880
Listen,

315
00:20:09,870 --> 00:20:11,630
the final results

316
00:20:12,160 --> 00:20:13,920
for your misconduct

317
00:20:14,190 --> 00:20:16,120
during the interrogation are out.

318
00:20:16,400 --> 00:20:18,460
You're getting a unit-wide warning.

319
00:20:18,470 --> 00:20:19,800
The suspension is over,

320
00:20:20,220 --> 00:20:22,640
but you've got a public self-criticism
at the end of the month.

321
00:20:22,640 --> 00:20:23,320
Really?

322
00:20:23,410 --> 00:20:24,920
You sound pretty happy about it.

323
00:20:24,920 --> 00:20:27,120
Of course. That means I'm back on the job.

324
00:20:27,120 --> 00:20:27,840
Report back

325
00:20:28,030 --> 00:20:28,880
this afternoon.

326
00:20:28,880 --> 00:20:29,410
Yes, sir.

327
00:20:32,320 --> 00:20:33,950
Is Professor Jiang with you?

328
00:20:33,990 --> 00:20:35,190
Yes. What is it?

329
00:20:35,190 --> 00:20:36,320
Put him on the phone.

330
00:20:36,850 --> 00:20:37,430
Okay.

331
00:20:38,510 --> 00:20:39,710
My mentor, Chief Tan.

332
00:20:43,080 --> 00:20:43,880
Chief Tan.

333
00:20:44,080 --> 00:20:45,410
This is Jiang Hansheng.

334
00:20:48,400 --> 00:20:49,560
You little pup.

335
00:20:49,880 --> 00:20:51,280
You've grown some wings.

336
00:20:51,590 --> 00:20:53,190
How dare you ignore my calls!

337
00:20:54,200 --> 00:20:54,790
Sir.

338
00:20:55,190 --> 00:20:56,920
Now you remember to call me Sir!

339
00:20:58,120 --> 00:20:59,120
Why are you there?

340
00:20:59,320 --> 00:21:00,400
Something happened.

341
00:21:00,400 --> 00:21:01,860
I'll tell you when we meet.

342
00:21:02,070 --> 00:21:02,680
Bring

343
00:21:03,130 --> 00:21:03,950
that little girl, Zhou,

344
00:21:03,950 --> 00:21:04,560
with you.

345
00:21:06,030 --> 00:21:06,510
Okay.

346
00:21:12,800 --> 00:21:13,800
Here.

347
00:21:15,030 --> 00:21:15,840
Sir.

348
00:21:16,400 --> 00:21:17,260
Director Wang?

349
00:21:18,540 --> 00:21:19,470
He's in Haizhou.

350
00:21:19,710 --> 00:21:20,770
He wants to see you.

351
00:21:20,950 --> 00:21:21,800
See me?

352
00:21:22,880 --> 00:21:24,280
Why does he want to see me?

353
00:21:27,410 --> 00:21:29,320
Should I prepare something for him?

354
00:21:29,320 --> 00:21:30,950
No need. He is a nice person.

355
00:21:34,180 --> 00:21:35,980
I heard him yelling you just now.

356
00:21:36,030 --> 00:21:37,270
Pup.

357
00:21:39,400 --> 00:21:41,320
Just think of it as a nickname.

358
00:21:42,880 --> 00:21:43,610
Don't laugh.

359
00:21:45,080 --> 00:21:45,630
Okay.

360
00:21:45,650 --> 00:21:46,780
I'll stop laughing.

361
00:21:47,710 --> 00:21:49,160
I'm going to change clothes.

362
00:21:49,160 --> 00:21:50,160
You should go too.

363
00:21:51,090 --> 00:21:52,020
Pup.

364
00:22:22,090 --> 00:22:22,700
Hansheng.

365
00:22:25,190 --> 00:22:26,920
I'll wash up and be ready soon.

366
00:22:27,750 --> 00:22:28,510
No rush.

367
00:22:56,860 --> 00:22:57,470
You're back.

368
00:22:57,470 --> 00:22:58,120
Dan.

369
00:22:58,800 --> 00:23:00,270
Chief Tan is waiting for you
in his office.

370
00:23:00,270 --> 00:23:01,230
Professor Jiang,

371
00:23:01,230 --> 00:23:02,220
Director Wang is in the reception room.

372
00:23:02,220 --> 00:23:03,350
I'll take you there.

373
00:23:04,710 --> 00:23:05,510
See you later.

374
00:23:09,920 --> 00:23:10,580
Reporting.

375
00:23:10,670 --> 00:23:11,160
Come in.

376
00:23:12,740 --> 00:23:13,220
Sir.

377
00:23:13,620 --> 00:23:14,680
Where is everyone?

378
00:23:15,450 --> 00:23:16,650
Do you think they are all like you,

379
00:23:16,650 --> 00:23:17,720
idling at home?

380
00:23:17,920 --> 00:23:19,120
They're busy as hell.

381
00:23:19,920 --> 00:23:21,250
I have a new case for you.

382
00:23:21,650 --> 00:23:23,230
Did we get a new lead on the 8.17 case?

383
00:23:23,230 --> 00:23:24,830
All you know is the 8.17 case.

384
00:23:25,030 --> 00:23:26,880
A homicide has occurred

385
00:23:26,990 --> 00:23:28,830
in Lishui Residential Area,
Lanjing Street.

386
00:23:28,830 --> 00:23:31,480
Based on the initial investigation
of the crime scene,

387
00:23:31,480 --> 00:23:32,660
it bears a strong resemblance

388
00:23:32,660 --> 00:23:34,360
to the two cases in Ningyuan and New Port

389
00:23:34,360 --> 00:23:35,490
earlier this month.

390
00:23:35,850 --> 00:23:37,240
You should go check out the crime scene.

391
00:23:37,240 --> 00:23:38,700
Is it a serial murder case?

392
00:23:38,840 --> 00:23:39,950
It's very likely.

393
00:23:40,670 --> 00:23:42,270
Director Wang Pengze is here

394
00:23:42,360 --> 00:23:43,510
for this case too.

395
00:23:44,030 --> 00:23:44,710
By the way,

396
00:23:45,590 --> 00:23:46,440
he personally

397
00:23:46,460 --> 00:23:48,220
requested you by name

398
00:23:48,250 --> 00:23:50,380
to participate in the investigation.

399
00:23:53,270 --> 00:23:54,230
Why me?

400
00:23:54,360 --> 00:23:55,320
How would I know?

401
00:23:55,930 --> 00:23:57,190
You'll have to ask him.

402
00:24:00,230 --> 00:24:02,290
Is there something you are afraid of?

403
00:24:03,080 --> 00:24:04,430
Hurry up and go.

404
00:24:08,370 --> 00:24:10,990
[Reception Room]

405
00:24:58,510 --> 00:24:59,790
Look who it is.

406
00:25:01,330 --> 00:25:04,010
It's the famous Professor Jiang.

407
00:25:05,160 --> 00:25:06,760
I've heard so much about you.

408
00:25:07,270 --> 00:25:08,840
If there's nothing important,

409
00:25:08,840 --> 00:25:10,640
you can just go back to sleeping.

410
00:25:11,450 --> 00:25:13,580
Just seeing you makes me angry
and gives me a headache.

411
00:25:13,580 --> 00:25:15,040
How am I supposed to sleep?

412
00:25:15,190 --> 00:25:16,400
You were snoring.

413
00:25:16,990 --> 00:25:18,320
Isn't it because of you?

414
00:25:18,510 --> 00:25:20,610
I told you to stay low in Haizhou

415
00:25:20,630 --> 00:25:22,150
and live a quiet life.

416
00:25:23,050 --> 00:25:24,460
But you had to do the opposite.

417
00:25:24,460 --> 00:25:26,920
You're almost a star now
in the police force.

418
00:25:29,880 --> 00:25:30,470
Sir.

419
00:25:31,600 --> 00:25:33,200
I'd love to live a quiet life.

420
00:25:34,070 --> 00:25:35,360
But they won't let me.

421
00:25:40,860 --> 00:25:43,550
[Two days ago]

422
00:25:50,640 --> 00:25:51,320
Sir.

423
00:25:52,920 --> 00:25:53,750
Pocket watch.

424
00:25:57,380 --> 00:25:58,780
They put the pocket watch

425
00:25:59,430 --> 00:26:01,230
next to Zhou Chuan's tombstone.

426
00:26:24,730 --> 00:26:25,590
Director Wang.

427
00:26:25,920 --> 00:26:26,640
Hello.

428
00:26:26,840 --> 00:26:29,110
I'm Zhou Jin, an investigator

429
00:26:29,230 --> 00:26:31,030
from the CIB of Nancheng Branch.

430
00:26:31,950 --> 00:26:32,990
Zhou.

431
00:26:35,560 --> 00:26:36,890
Hansheng is my student.

432
00:26:37,160 --> 00:26:38,490
So that makes us family.

433
00:26:38,980 --> 00:26:40,370
He always talks about you.

434
00:26:40,370 --> 00:26:41,840
I finally get to meet you today.

435
00:26:41,840 --> 00:26:43,440
You're just like I imagined.

436
00:26:43,510 --> 00:26:44,320
Excellent.

437
00:26:44,360 --> 00:26:45,810
Very good.

438
00:26:46,640 --> 00:26:47,060
Director Wang.

439
00:26:47,060 --> 00:26:49,560
Hansheng and I should have been the ones
to visit you.

440
00:26:49,560 --> 00:26:50,690
I'm just an old man.

441
00:26:51,080 --> 00:26:52,210
What's there to see?

442
00:26:53,200 --> 00:26:54,780
I used to work in criminal investigation.

443
00:26:54,780 --> 00:26:57,040
I know how hard you are
on the front lines.

444
00:26:57,320 --> 00:26:59,110
Visiting or not isn't important.

445
00:26:59,110 --> 00:27:00,330
The important thing is

446
00:27:00,330 --> 00:27:01,800
you need to care for him more

447
00:27:01,800 --> 00:27:03,080
and be a bit more patient

448
00:27:03,080 --> 00:27:04,320
with this silly boy.

449
00:27:08,920 --> 00:27:11,520
Captain Tan has briefed you on the case,
right?

450
00:27:11,970 --> 00:27:13,630
He filled me in on everything.

451
00:27:14,240 --> 00:27:15,810
This is a major case.

452
00:27:16,240 --> 00:27:17,570
I came to Haizhou alone.

453
00:27:17,760 --> 00:27:19,180
I need someone from your team

454
00:27:19,180 --> 00:27:20,220
to work with me.

455
00:27:20,640 --> 00:27:22,090
I've thought it over,

456
00:27:23,600 --> 00:27:25,270
and I think you're the right person.

457
00:27:25,270 --> 00:27:27,750
Also, Hansheng, as my student,

458
00:27:28,200 --> 00:27:30,660
will participate in the investigation too.

459
00:27:31,430 --> 00:27:32,140
Sir,

460
00:27:32,440 --> 00:27:33,410
what kind of case

461
00:27:33,570 --> 00:27:35,500
would bring you to the front lines?

462
00:27:36,190 --> 00:27:38,450
You'll know once you see the crime scene.

463
00:27:38,580 --> 00:27:39,650
I came here at 8 this morning.

464
00:27:39,650 --> 00:27:40,250
At 8.

465
00:27:40,250 --> 00:27:41,930
Have you delivered packages to her before?

466
00:27:41,930 --> 00:27:42,970
Yes, I have.

467
00:27:43,250 --> 00:27:45,060
Do you know the homeowner's name?

468
00:27:45,060 --> 00:27:46,100
No, I don't.

469
00:27:46,100 --> 00:27:46,890
Jin,

470
00:27:47,060 --> 00:27:48,190
you're back on duty?

471
00:27:49,620 --> 00:27:50,780
Excuse me, everyone. Coming through.

472
00:27:50,780 --> 00:27:52,310
Excuse me, coming through.

473
00:27:53,450 --> 00:27:54,520
Has the body been taken away?

474
00:27:54,520 --> 00:27:56,450
Not yet. Dr. Lin is still upstairs.

475
00:27:56,710 --> 00:27:58,780
Right on time, Director Wang. We're ready.

476
00:27:58,780 --> 00:28:00,670
Please head up to the second floor
and take a look.

477
00:28:00,670 --> 00:28:01,060
Okay.

478
00:28:01,340 --> 00:28:02,170
Let's go upstairs.

479
00:28:02,170 --> 00:28:03,320
Yes, this way.

480
00:28:33,550 --> 00:28:34,200
Lin.

481
00:28:34,460 --> 00:28:35,670
Suicide or homicide?

482
00:28:35,830 --> 00:28:36,630
Homicide.

483
00:28:43,620 --> 00:28:46,280
It has a strong emotional
and ritualistic tone.

484
00:28:46,590 --> 00:28:47,740
It's quite creepy.

485
00:29:16,360 --> 00:29:17,050
Have you taken pictures?

486
00:29:17,050 --> 00:29:17,640
Yes.

487
00:29:42,150 --> 00:29:44,680
If there's only
a single incision on the wrist

488
00:29:44,870 --> 00:29:47,400
with no other
superficial hesitation marks,

489
00:29:47,430 --> 00:29:48,490
it means the killer

490
00:29:48,500 --> 00:29:50,260
only made one cut.

491
00:29:51,170 --> 00:29:53,970
But there's no significant bloodstain
by the bed.

492
00:29:55,090 --> 00:29:57,090
This isn't the primary crime scene.

493
00:29:58,500 --> 00:29:59,480
It's the bathroom, right?

494
00:29:59,480 --> 00:29:59,960
Yes.

495
00:31:15,340 --> 00:31:17,670
No.

496
00:31:23,670 --> 00:31:24,280
No.

497
00:31:26,020 --> 00:31:26,540
No.

498
00:31:26,910 --> 00:31:27,590
Please.

499
00:31:28,230 --> 00:31:29,380
I'm begging.

500
00:31:29,910 --> 00:31:30,430
No.

501
00:31:30,500 --> 00:31:30,910
No.

502
00:31:33,750 --> 00:31:34,300
No.

503
00:31:35,860 --> 00:31:36,700
No!

504
00:32:06,890 --> 00:32:07,530
Hansheng.

505
00:32:17,030 --> 00:32:17,470
Jin.

506
00:32:21,640 --> 00:32:23,620
We've pretty much got all the information.

507
00:32:23,620 --> 00:32:24,880
The victim's name is Zhao Xiaoyu.

508
00:32:24,880 --> 00:32:26,610
She's 27 years old. Unmarried.

509
00:32:26,750 --> 00:32:28,360
Her parents bought this apartment for her,

510
00:32:28,360 --> 00:32:29,860
and she usually lived here alone.

511
00:32:29,860 --> 00:32:31,060
When was it reported?

512
00:32:31,510 --> 00:32:32,470
This morning.

513
00:32:32,670 --> 00:32:34,860
The person who reported it
is the delivery guy downstairs.

514
00:32:34,860 --> 00:32:35,820
Before Zhao Xiaoyu died,

515
00:32:35,820 --> 00:32:37,420
she ordered flowers online.

516
00:32:37,540 --> 00:32:38,190
Every Monday,

517
00:32:38,190 --> 00:32:40,190
a delivery guy would deliver them
to her door.

518
00:32:40,190 --> 00:32:41,710
Today, when the delivery guy arrived,

519
00:32:41,710 --> 00:32:42,910
he noticed the door was unlocked.

520
00:32:42,910 --> 00:32:44,510
He intended to come in just to remind her,

521
00:32:44,510 --> 00:32:45,750
but as soon as he stepped inside,

522
00:32:45,750 --> 00:32:46,780
he noticed a strange smell.

523
00:32:46,780 --> 00:32:48,110
So he called the police.

524
00:32:48,790 --> 00:32:50,050
We're heading off now.

525
00:32:50,430 --> 00:32:51,030
Take care.

526
00:32:57,990 --> 00:32:59,230
Have the family been notified?

527
00:32:59,230 --> 00:32:59,910
Yes.

528
00:33:00,140 --> 00:33:01,140
Her parents are out of town.

529
00:33:01,140 --> 00:33:03,070
They won't be here until tomorrow.

530
00:33:04,190 --> 00:33:05,780
Director Wang compared the scenes.

531
00:33:05,780 --> 00:33:06,550
He said

532
00:33:06,780 --> 00:33:09,620
it seems like the same killer
as in Ningyuan and New Port.

533
00:33:09,620 --> 00:33:10,340
I heard.

534
00:33:10,950 --> 00:33:12,150
A serial murder case.

535
00:33:12,380 --> 00:33:14,580
The smell of disinfectant is so strong.

536
00:33:14,580 --> 00:33:15,980
And the scene is so clean.

537
00:33:16,100 --> 00:33:17,000
The killer really

538
00:33:17,000 --> 00:33:19,060
cleaned up the scene very carefully.

539
00:33:19,300 --> 00:33:20,700
The MO is highly skilled.

540
00:33:20,990 --> 00:33:22,340
The target is very clear.

541
00:33:22,340 --> 00:33:23,940
And it's a mobile operation.

542
00:33:24,540 --> 00:33:27,510
This has completely stepped
outside the psychological safety zone.

543
00:33:27,510 --> 00:33:28,620
The killer is very dangerous.

544
00:33:28,620 --> 00:33:30,240
We must catch him as soon as possible.

545
00:33:30,240 --> 00:33:31,620
In terms of criminal features,

546
00:33:31,620 --> 00:33:32,820
these three cases

547
00:33:33,030 --> 00:33:34,620
are very similar

548
00:33:34,620 --> 00:33:35,990
to the Huaiguang serial murder case.

549
00:33:35,990 --> 00:33:37,150
The signature elements such as

550
00:33:37,150 --> 00:33:38,100
women in red dresses,

551
00:33:38,100 --> 00:33:38,710
roses,

552
00:33:38,860 --> 00:33:39,390
and bows,

553
00:33:40,540 --> 00:33:42,470
as well as his handling of the scenes,

554
00:33:42,470 --> 00:33:43,930
the posture of the bodies,

555
00:33:43,950 --> 00:33:45,880
and the fatal wounds on the wrists.

556
00:33:47,100 --> 00:33:48,100
They are the same.

557
00:33:49,910 --> 00:33:50,430
But...

558
00:33:50,670 --> 00:33:51,750
But five years ago,

559
00:33:52,270 --> 00:33:54,670
the killer of the Huaiguang serial murders

560
00:33:54,800 --> 00:33:56,450
was already shot dead by you!

561
00:33:59,230 --> 00:34:00,030
Not only that.

562
00:34:01,540 --> 00:34:03,000
It's not exactly the same.

563
00:34:03,920 --> 00:34:04,850
What do you mean?

564
00:34:05,510 --> 00:34:06,060
The bows.

565
00:34:07,040 --> 00:34:08,540
Although they are all bows,

566
00:34:08,540 --> 00:34:10,040
they're tied in different ways.

567
00:34:10,040 --> 00:34:12,570
Especially this one.
It's a three-layer bow.

568
00:34:12,719 --> 00:34:14,250
It's very difficult to tie.

569
00:34:14,370 --> 00:34:16,570
But he tied it perfectly, full and neat.

570
00:34:19,020 --> 00:34:19,719
This kind of bow

571
00:34:19,719 --> 00:34:22,280
is only used

572
00:34:22,389 --> 00:34:24,050
when giving a gift to someone.

573
00:34:28,429 --> 00:34:30,330
Could this be his gift to Qi Yan?

574
00:34:32,540 --> 00:34:34,719
The details of Qi Yan's cases

575
00:34:35,659 --> 00:34:37,179
are not fully disclosed.

576
00:34:37,469 --> 00:34:38,290
How could he

577
00:34:38,310 --> 00:34:38,909
imitate it

578
00:34:38,989 --> 00:34:40,060
to this extent?

579
00:34:41,510 --> 00:34:42,510
It's impossible.

580
00:34:43,790 --> 00:34:45,320
Do you think he knows Qi Yan?

581
00:34:47,659 --> 00:34:48,690
Rather than saying

582
